Package src.user_data

Class Student

java.lang.Object
src.user_data.User
src.user_data.Student
Direct Known Subclasses:
CampCommittee
public class Student extends User
The Student class represents a student user in the system, extending the base User class. It includes information about camps the student is registered for, available camps, withdrawn camps, enquiries made, and committee status.
